          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="touch-target-size" class="doc-h3">Touch Target Size</h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Interactive elements within the inline alert must meet minimum touch target requirements.</p>
            <div style="margin-top:16px;padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;">
              <div style="width:44px;height:44px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);border:1px dashed var(--prism-violet);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--prism-violet);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0;">44px</div>
              <div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--prism-text);">Dismiss Button: 44&times;44px minimum touch area</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">While the dismiss icon is 16&#215;16px visually, ensure the tappable area extends to at least 44&#215;44px using padding or an invisible hit area. The action link should also meet the 44px minimum touch target.</div></div>
            </div>
